00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:15.550
Teach Students to Ask Their
Own Questions, the book,

00:00:15.550 --> 00:00:19.620
which first introduced the
Question Formulation Technique.

00:00:19.620 --> 00:00:25.250 position:63%
Dan's work focuses on honoring and
supporting the work of 200,000 educators

00:00:25.250 --> 00:00:31.540 position:70%
