people in the private sector,

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:34.430
in Warren Berger's book,
A More Beautiful Question.

00:03:34.430 --> 00:03:38.490
He featured the strategy as
a way to promote innovation.

00:03:38.490 --> 00:03:43.010 position:70%
